replyContent: I strongly disagree that the free version is "so riddled with ads as to be unusable". The ads are small and only shown at the bottom of some pages, there are no full page ads which many other apps do have. Alarms will be available in an upcoming version and our graphics, such as the sky chart, have been well received and will be further improved.

content: Live sky view and time line view, coupled with the fact that calculations are performed locally are the best features, hard to find on other apps. Chris is a pro and this app is worth every cent!
